        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 5. Dichotomius belus (Harold, 1880). A–B. Dorsal habitus. A. ♁. B. ♀. C. Lateral view of the aedeagus. D. Anterior view of the shape of the cephalic carina. E. Ventral view of the aedeagus. F–G. Lamella copulatrix. H. Lateral view, showing the pronotum and the cephalic carina flattened antero-posteriorly and curved anteriorly." ;
